{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"445","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"聯合國報告：2018極端天氣侵襲6200萬人","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>聯合國氣象機構表示，隨著人為導致的氣候變遷惡化，去年極端天氣侵襲全球6200萬人，迫使200萬人搬遷。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>世界氣象組織（World Meteorological Organization, WMO）公布的年度全球氣候報告指出，與工業時代初期相比，現今地球溫度升高將近華氏1.8度（攝氏1度）。各國領導人試圖把升溫幅度控制在華氏3.6度（攝氏2度）。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>美聯社報導，為了發電和提供交通工具動力，燃燒煤炭、汽油和柴油等燃料排放的二氧化碳，促使全球暖化，進而使暴風雨、洪水和乾旱更加劇烈。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>世界氣象組織秘書長塔拉斯（Petteri Taalas）說：「由於氣候變遷，災害的頻率不斷提高。」他指出，自1998年以來，全球約有45億人因極端天氣受害。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>塔拉斯表示，剛侵襲莫三比克的熱帶氣旋伊代（Idai）就是一個絕佳例子，但由於近期發生，來不及寫進報告。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>根據這份報告，過去4年是紀錄中氣溫最高的一段時間。塔拉斯指出，其中包括紀錄中溫度最高的2018反聖嬰年。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>聯合國秘書長古特瑞斯（Antonio Guterres）呼籲全球各國領導人，9月帶著減碳計畫出席會議。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>古特瑞斯說：「我告訴這些領導人，不要來演講而已，要有（減碳）計畫。」</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>他說，氣候變遷是全球安全和健康問題。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: custom-sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;SF Pro TC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;'>他並說：「氣候變遷對公共衛生的影響越來越大，極度高溫連同空氣汙染的危險性已證明是與日俱增。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/201903290243.aspx</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-04-15","clk_count":"61"}},"__N_SSG":true}